**Checking if a bit is set:**
```java
if ((flags & 0x04) != 0) {
    // Third bit is set
}
```

**Setting specific bits:**
```java
flags |= 0x08;  // Set 4th bit
flags &= ~0x02; // Clear 2nd bit
```

**RGB to Integer:**
```java
int color = (r << 16) | (g << 8) | b;
// Example: RGB(255, 87, 51)
// = (FF << 16) | (57 << 8) | 33
// = 0xFF5733
```

**Extracting RGB values:**
```java
int red = (color >> 16) & 0xFF;
int green = (color >> 8) & 0xFF;
int blue = color & 0xFF;
```

**Quick power of 2 check:**
```java
boolean isPowerOf2 = (n & (n-1)) == 0;
// Works because powers of 2 have only one bit set
```
